      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just a pause, though. even when i stop working, the thoughts don't stop. the pressure is just... it's constant. it's in my head 24/7. i feel like i'm just performing this version of a person that's constantly drowning, and everyone expects me to just keep swimming. i'm just so beyond exhausted. i don't think a weekend off or a vacation is going to fix the fact that my entire life has just become a void. i just want the noise to finally stop. permanently.",
